Putting this all together leads to the very simple formula for the
three-point function at  () C(_1,_2,_3)e^-i_1X^0 e^-i_1X^0 e^-i_1X^0  =-(_R )^i(_1+_2+_3) e^-(_1+_2+_3)/2 . As a check
